---
// Hero.astro
---

<section class="h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden bg-black space-y-6">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-blob"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/3 w-96 h-96 bg-pink-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="container px-4 mx-auto text-center z-20">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold mb-10 z-10 leading-tight">
        <span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Samuel Sotomayor
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 z-2">
       Desarrollador web con una gran motivaci√≥n para crear y realizar proyectos desafiantes.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center relative z-20">
        <a
          href="#projects"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-blue-600 text-white font-medium flex items-center"
        >
          View Projects
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 hover:bg-zinc-900 font-medium"
        >
          Contact Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="h-6 w-6 rotate-90 text-zinc-500"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
      >
        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>
  